{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Game Overview</h2>In the game &quot;Xia Luo: Kill All Flowers&quot;, you will play a criminal and enter a dark and eerie world, experiencing an unprecedented strange adventure.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Meet Xiake</h2>In this extreme world, there are still some people who spare no effort in practicing their own &quot;chivalry&quot; at all costs, and people call them &quot;heroes&quot;. Get to know them and embark on an adventure together in this strange world!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Free exploration</h2>You can lead your team to freely explore on the map, experience the ups and downs of the main storyline and various side storylines. Numerous bizarre people and events will take turns on your adventure, and various conspiracies and mysteries will be revealed by you personally.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">A brand new battle</h2>The battles in this game incorporate the commonly used &quot;dice element&quot; in board games, attempting to create a new turn based combat experience. Whether it's a steady and steady fight or a small and broad one, it's all in your mind.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Strategy combination</h2>Each hero in this game has over a hundred skills, paired with freely chosen talents and a plethora of equipment entries. You can create unique combat routines according to your personal combat preferences, dominating the world.","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2774390/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1723128468","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2774390/page.bg.jpg?t=1723128468","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2774390/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1723128468","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2774390/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1723128468","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22},{"description":"Steam Clou